summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain property and property rights necessary for sanitary sewer purposes in the Amended Replat Of A Portion Of Spring Hill Villa Tracts, "Park Reserve". . . . Rosenbaum Spring Hill Addition No. 2, Plat of Lincoln Beach, and of Second Class Tide Lands adjoining said plats, and for a watermain appurtenant to said sewers, . . . , all as a part of certain additions and betterments to the existing municipal sewerage utility and providing for payment therefor.
